    </div>
    
    <b>HTML Structure:</b>
    <div style="background-color: #e0e0e0; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <pre>
            &lt;div class="poster"&gt;
                &lt;h1 class="main-title"&gt;CSS Typography&lt;/h1&gt;
                &lt;h2 class="subtitle"&gt;The Art of Beautiful Text&lt;/h2&gt;
                &lt;p class="quote"&gt;"Good typography is invisible. Bad typography is everywhere."&lt;/p&gt;
