    <b>d. Margin Collapse - The "Space Merging" Quirk</b><br/>
    
    <b>When vertical margins collapse:</b>
    <div style="background-color: #e0e0e0; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <pre>
