        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">animation-timing-function</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Speed curve</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">ease, linear, cubic-bezier()</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">ease</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">animation-delay</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Wait before starting</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">time (s, ms)</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">0s</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">animation-iteration-count</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">How many times to play</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">number, infinite</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">1</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">animation-direction</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Play direction</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">normal, reverse, alternate, alternate-reverse</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">normal</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">animation-fill-mode</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Styles before/after</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">none, forwards, backwards, both</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">none</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">animation-play-state</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Running or paused</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">running, paused</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">running</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <hr/>
    
    <b>c. Transform Properties for Animation</b>
    
    <div style="background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <b>CSS Transform Functions:</b><br/>
        ‚Ä¢ translate(x, y): Move element<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ translateX(x), translateY(y): Move on one axis<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ scale(x, y): Resize element<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ scaleX(x), scaleY(y): Scale on one axis<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ rotate(angle): Rotate element<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ skew(x-angle, y-angle): Skew element<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ skewX(angle), skewY(angle): Skew on one axis<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ matrix(a, b, c, d, tx, ty): Complex transformations<br/><br/>
        
        <b>Transform Origin:</b><br/>
        ‚Ä¢ transform-origin: x y z;<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ Controls the point around which transforms occur<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ Default: center center (50% 50%)
    </div>
    
    <div style="background-color: #e0e0e0; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <b>Transform Examples:</b><br/>
        <pre>
            /* Basic transforms */
            .element {
                transform: translate(50px, 100px);
            }
            
            /* Multiple transforms (applied in order!) */
            .element {
                transform: translateX(50px) rotate(45deg) scale(1.2);
            }
            
            /* 3D transforms */
            .element {
                transform: perspective(500px) rotateY(45deg);
                transform-style: preserve-3d;
                backface-visibility: hidden;
            }
            
            /* Transform origin examples */
            .rotate-top-left {
                transform-origin: top left;
                transform: rotate(45deg);
            }
            
            .scale-from-center {
                transform-origin: center center;
                transform: scale(1.5);
            }
        </pre>
    </div>
    
    <hr/>
    
    <b>d. Performance Considerations</b>
    
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <div style="background-color: #e8f5e8; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px;">
            <b>High Performance Properties (GPU accelerated):</b><br/>
            ‚Ä¢ transform: translate(), scale(), rotate()<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ opacity<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ filter<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ will-change (hint to browser)<br/><br/>
            
            <b>Tips for Smooth Animations:</b><br/>
            1. Use transform and opacity for animations<br/>
            2. Avoid animating width/height (use scale instead)<br/>
            3. Use will-change sparingly<br/>
            4. Keep animations under 100ms for UI, 200-500ms for page transitions<br/>
            5. Use requestAnimationFrame for JavaScript animations
        </div>
        
        <div style="background-color: #ffe6e6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px;">
            <b>Properties to Avoid Animating:</b><br/>
            ‚Ä¢ width, height (causes layout recalculation)<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ top, left, right, bottom (causes layout)<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ margin, padding (causes layout)<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ display (can't be animated)<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ font-size (causes layout and text reflow)<br/><br/>
            
            <b>Performance Impact:</b><br/>
            Layout ‚Üí Paint ‚Üí Composite<br/>
            (Most expensive) ‚Üí (Least expensive)
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background-color: #e0e0e0; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <b>Performance Example:</b><br/>
        <pre>
            /* ‚ùå BAD - Animates layout properties */
            .slow-animation {
                ;transition: width 0.3s ease, height 0.3s ease;
            }
            .slow-animation:hover {
                ;width: 200px;
                ;height: 200px;
            }
            
            /* ‚úÖ GOOD - Uses transform instead */
            .fast-animation {
                ;transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            }
            .fast-animation:hover {
                ;transform: scale(1.5);
            }
            
            /* ‚úÖ BETTER - Uses will-change hint */
            .optimized-animation {
                ;will-change: transform, opacity;
                ;transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            }
        </pre>
    </div>
    
