    <h3>Hands-On Exercises</h3>
    
    <b>Exercise 1: Create a Loading Spinner</b>
    
    <div style="background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <b>Task:</b> Create an animated loading spinner using CSS keyframes.<br/><br/>
        
        <b>Requirements:</b><br/>
