    <div style="background-color: #e8f5e8; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <h3>üéØ Day 1 Key Takeaways:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><b>Transitions</b> are for simple state changes, <b>keyframes</b> are for complex sequences</li>
            <li>Use <b>transform and opacity</b> for high-performance animations</li>
