    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <div style="background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px;">
            <b>CSS Properties That Work on SVG:</b><br/>
            ‚Ä¢ All animation and transition properties<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ transform (translate, rotate, scale, skew)<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ opacity<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ filter (drop-shadow, blur, etc.)<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ fill, stroke, stroke-width<br/>
