            ‚Ä¢ stroke-linecap, stroke-linejoin<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ visibility, display<br/><br/>
            
            <b>Note:</b> Some properties like <pre>background-color</pre> don't work on SVG elements
        </div>
        
        <div style="background-color: #fff0f0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px;">
            <b>Transform Origin in SVG:</b><br/>
            ‚Ä¢ SVG uses its own coordinate system<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ transform-origin works differently<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ Can use percentages or pixels<br/>
            ‚Ä¢ Default is 0 0 (top-left of SVG)<br/><br/>
            
            <pre>
