    <div style="background-color: #fff0f0; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <b>SMIL = Synchronized Multimedia Integration Language</b><br/>
        ‚Ä¢ Built-in SVG animation system<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ More powerful than CSS for some animations<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ Browser support concerns (deprecated in Chrome)<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ Still useful for complex SVG animations<br/><br/>
        
        <b>SMIL Animation Elements:</b><br/>
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;animate&gt;: Basic property animation<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;animateTransform&gt;: Transform animations<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;animateMotion&gt;: Motion along a path<br/>
        ‚Ä¢ &lt;set&gt;: Discrete property changes
    </div>
    
    <div style="background-color: #e0e0e0; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <b>SMIL Examples:</b><br/>
        <pre>
            &lt;!-- Animate attribute --&gt;
            &lt;circle cx="100" cy="100" r="50" fill="blue"&gt;
                &lt;animate attributeName="r" from="50" to="70" dur="2s" repeatCount="indefinite" /&gt;
            &lt;/circle&gt;
            
            &lt;!-- Animate transform --&gt;
            &lt;rect x="50" y="50" width="100" height="100" fill="green"&gt;
                &lt;animateTransform attributeName="transform" type="rotate" from="0 100 100" to="360 100 100" dur="3s" repeatCount="indefinite" /&gt;
            &lt;/rect&gt;
            
            &lt;!-- Animate along path --&gt;
            &lt;circle r="10" fill="red"&gt;
