                html: `<h1>Week 8, Day 3: Dynamic Styling with Classes</h1>
    <p>Today we'll learn how to dynamically change the appearance of web pages by adding, removing, and toggling CSS classes with JavaScript.</p>
    
    <div class="analogy-box">
