        <pre>CSS Classes</pre>: Different costumes for different scenes<br/>
        <pre>classList</pre>: Wardrobe with all available costumes<br/>
        <pre>add()</pre>: Putting on a new costume piece<br/>
        <pre>remove()</pre>: Taking off a costume piece<br/>
