                html: `<h1>Week 9, Day 1: Building Interactive Dashboards - Part 1</h1>
<p>Today we start our Level 2 Project: Building an interactive dashboard. This project will combine all the skills you've learned so far - HTML structure, CSS styling, JavaScript logic, and DOM manipulation.</p>

<div class="analogy-box">
    <b>Analogy: The Command Center üöÄ</b><br/>
    
