    <pre>State Management</pre>: Remembering user preferences and settings
</div>

<h3>Project Overview: Personal Finance Dashboard</h3>
<p>We'll build a dashboard to track personal finances with these features:</p>

<div style="background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
    <b>Core Components:</b>
    <ol>
        <li><b>Expense Tracker:</b> Add, categorize, and view expenses</li>
        <li><b>Budget Overview:</b> Visual budget vs actual spending</li>
        <li><b>Income Sources:</b> Track different income streams</li>
        <li><b>Savings Goals:</b> Progress bars for financial goals</li>
        <li><b>Charts & Graphs:</b> Visual data representation</li>
        <li><b>Notifications:</b> Alerts for budget limits</li>
        <li><b>Reports:</b> Monthly/Yearly financial summaries</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<h3>Setting Up the Project Structure</h3>

<b>HTML Structure (dashboard.html):</b>
<div style="background-color: #e0e0e0; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
<pre>
&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html lang="en"&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
    &lt;meta charset="UTF-8"&gt;
    &lt;meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;Personal Finance Dashboard&lt;/title&gt;
    &lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="dashboard.css"&gt;
    &lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
    &lt;div class="dashboard-container"&gt;
        &lt;!-- Sidebar Navigation --&gt;
        &lt;nav class="sidebar"&gt;
            &lt;div class="logo"&gt;
                &lt;i class="fas fa-chart-pie"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
                &lt;span&gt;FinanceDash&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;ul class="nav-menu"&gt;
                &lt;li class="active"&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-home"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Dashboard&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-wallet"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Expenses&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Income&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-bullseye"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Goals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-chart-bar"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Reports&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-cog"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Settings&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/nav&gt;

        &lt;!-- Main Content Area --&gt;
        &lt;main class="main-content"&gt;
            &lt;header class="top-bar"&gt;
                &lt;div class="search-bar"&gt;
                    &lt;i class="fas fa-search"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
                    &lt;input type="text" placeholder="Search transactions..."&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;div class="user-info"&gt;
                    &lt;div class="notification"&gt;
                        &lt;i class="fas fa-bell"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
                        &lt;span class="badge"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;div class="user-avatar"&gt;
                        &lt;img src="https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=John+Doe&amp;background=4A90E2&amp;color=fff" alt="User"&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/header&gt;

            &lt;!-- Dashboard Overview --&gt;
            &lt;section class="overview"&gt;
                &lt;h1&gt;Dashboard Overview&lt;/h1&gt;
                &lt;div class="stats-grid"&gt;
                    &lt;div class="stat-card income"&gt;
                        &lt;div class="stat-icon"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
                        &lt;div class="stat-info"&gt;
                            &lt;h3&gt;Total Income&lt;/h3&gt;
                            &lt;p class="amount" id="total-income"&gt;$0.00&lt;/p&gt;
                            &lt;span class="trend positive"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-arrow-up"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; 12%&lt;/span&gt;
                        &lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;

                    &lt;div class="stat-card expenses"&gt;
                        &lt;div class="stat-icon"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
                        &lt;div class="stat-info"&gt;
                            &lt;h3&gt;Total Expenses&lt;/h3&gt;
                            &lt;p class="amount" id="total-expenses"&gt;$0.00&lt;/p&gt;
                            &lt;span class="trend negative"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-arrow-down"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; 5%&lt;/span&gt;
                        &lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;

                    &lt;div class="stat-card savings"&gt;
                        &lt;div class="stat-icon"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-piggy-bank"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
                        &lt;div class="stat-info"&gt;
                            &lt;h3&gt;Total Savings&lt;/h3&gt;
                            &lt;p class="amount" id="total-savings"&gt;$0.00&lt;/p&gt;
                            &lt;span class="trend positive"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-arrow-up"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; 8%&lt;/span&gt;
                        &lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;

                    &lt;div class="stat-card budget"&gt;
                        &lt;div class="stat-icon"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-chart-line"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
                        &lt;div class="stat-info"&gt;
