        <li><b>Data Types:</b> Choosing appropriate types for different data</li>
        <li><b>Schema Design:</b> Creating logical, normalized database structures</li>
        <li><b>Foreign Keys:</b> Establishing relationships between tables</li>
        <li><b>Indexes:</b> Understanding how indexes improve query performance</li>
        <li><b>Basic Operations:</b> Creating, describing, and managing databases</li>
