                    </div>
                    
                    <div>
                        <h5 style="margin-top: 0;">Advanced Queries (5):</h5>
                        <ol style="font-size: 14px;" start="11">
                            <li>Year-over-year spending comparison</li>
                            <li>Anomaly detection (unusual transactions)</li>
                            <li>Budget vs actual analysis</li>
