    <b>Requirements:</b>
    <div style="background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        1. Display products in a responsive grid/table<br/>
        2. Include product image, name, price, category, and stock status<br/>
        3. Add search functionality (by name, category, price range)<br/>
        4. Implement pagination (10 products per page)<br/>
        5. Add sorting options (price low-high, new arrivals, name A-Z)<br/>
        6. Show "Out of Stock" badge for products with 0 quantity<br/>
        7. Add "Sale" badge for products with price reductions<br/>
