            <th style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">When to Use</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><b>SFTP</b><br/>(SSH File Transfer Protocol)</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Uses SSH encryption, single connection</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">22</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">‚úÖ Excellent (SSH encryption)</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Modern servers, most secure option</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><b>FTPS</b><br/>(FTP over SSL/TLS)</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">FTP with SSL/TLS encryption</td>
