    <b>Requirements:</b>
    <div style="background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        1. <b>HTTPS Implementation:</b><br/>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;- Obtain and install Let's Encrypt SSL certificate<br/>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;- Configure web server for HTTPS<br/>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;- Implement HTTP to HTTPS redirect<br/>
