        <br/>
        2. <b>Security Headers:</b><br/>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;- Implement CSP, X-Frame-Options, X-XSS-Protection<br/>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;- Add Referrer-Policy and Permissions-Policy<br/>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;- Configure proper caching headers<br/>
