        3. <b>Application Security:</b><br/>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;- Implement CSRF protection with tokens<br/>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;- Secure session management<br/>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;- Add SQL injection protection<br/>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;- Implement XSS protection<br/>
        <br/>
        4. <b>Server Hardening:</b><br/>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;- Disable unnecessary services<br/>
